Team B Turnover: (Team A TOV% - Team B TOV%D) - (Team B TOV% - Team A TOV%D)

Team A Rebounding: (Team A ORB% - Team B DRB%) - (Team B ORB% - Team A DRB%)
Team B Rebounding: (Team B ORB% - Team A DRB%) - (Team A ORB% - Team B DRB%)

Team A Free Throw: (Team A FTr - Team B FTrD) - (Team B FTr - Team A FTrD)
Team B Free Throw: (Team B FTr - Team A FTrD) - (Team A FTr - Team B FTrD)

Team A Total: (0.4 * Team A Shooting + 0.25 * Team A Turnover + 0.2 * Team A Rebounding + 0.15 * Team A Free Throw)
Team B Total: (0.4 * Team B Shooting + 0.25 * Team B Turnover + 0.2 * Team B Rebounding + 0.15 * Team B Free Throw)
